ComposaPy.DataFlow.models¶

Classes

DataFlowObject(contract, service)

DataFlowObject can be used to both model and save dataflow configurations, both saved and before saving.

DataFlowRun(contract)

Similar to a DataFlowObject, with a couple of differences.

DataFlowRunSet(dataflow_runs)

Wrapper for dataflow run objects, using ObjectSetMixin convenience mixin utilities.

Input(contract)

Wraps ModuleIn contract for a simplified textual user interface.

Module(contract)

The object representation of a module inside a dataflow object.

ModuleSet(modules)

Wrapper for objects with parent Module, for convenience methods on the set of items contained with self._target.

Result(contract)

Wraps ModuleOut contract for a simplified textual user interface.

ResultModule(contract)

Extends Module to give the ability to retrieve module results.

Exceptions

ModuleResultError
